window.bookSummaryJSON = "Gene Wilder was nominated for a Best Supporting Actor Oscar for his role as Leo Bloom in <i>The Producers</i>. That led to a role in <i>Blazing Saddles</i> and to another Academy Award nomination, this time for writing <i>Young Frankenstein</i>. His memoir, <i>Kiss Me Like a Stranger</i>, was a best seller. Wilder has also written his first novel, <i>My French Whore</i>, an intimate love story set inside a classic spy adventure."; 
